# The vendored SpecKit tree is hashed by .specify/integrations/*.manifest.json
# (SHA-256 of each managed file, as written by SpecKit's installer with LF line
# endings). The drift check (scripts/check-speckit-drift.*) re-hashes the
# WORKING-TREE files, so line endings must survive checkout unchanged on every
# platform — otherwise a Windows clone with core.autocrlf=true would rewrite
# LF->CRLF and report false drift. Force LF for everything under speckit/.
* text eol=lf
